trans-unit.source: Provides a delegate with which ASP.NET extracts a set of name/value pairs from an <xref href="System.Web.UI.IBindableTemplate"></xref> object at run time.
trans-unit.target: 与 ASP.NET 提取中的名称/值对一组将委托提供<xref href="System.Web.UI.IBindableTemplate"></xref>在运行时的对象。

trans-unit.source: The ExtractTemplateValuesMethod delegate is used by ASP.NET and is not meant to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: ExtractTemplateValuesMethod 委托可供 ASP.NET 并不是在代码中直接使用。

trans-unit.source: This delegate is used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.CompiledBindableTemplateBuilder> class, which is the default implementation of the <xref:System.Web.UI.IBindableTemplate> interface that ASP.NET generates when the ASP.NET parser encounters two-way data-binding within templated content.
trans-unit.target: 通过使用此委托<xref:System.Web.UI.CompiledBindableTemplateBuilder>类，它是默认实现的<xref:System.Web.UI.IBindableTemplate>ASP.NET 分析器在遇到在模板化的内容中的双向数据绑定 ASP.NET 生成的接口。</xref:System.Web.UI.IBindableTemplate> </xref:System.Web.UI.CompiledBindableTemplateBuilder>
